Package: Saqrlab
Title: Simulation and Analysis for Temporal Network Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mohammed", "Saqr", email = "saqr@saqr.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for simulating Markov chain sequences, bootstrapping temporal
    network models, and evaluating edge recovery performance. Supports multiple
    TNA model variants (tna, ftna, ctna, atna) with parallel processing capabilities.
